Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Truth of the Ishtars Revealed"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Ra card been translated yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I linked to Industrial Illusion's central computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's in the process of deciphering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can understand what this text says!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it tells about Ra's Special Abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's terrifying...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those letters are Hieratic Text!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The {\b0}chosen ones{\b1} can\N read it with their {\b0}hearts{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one standing beside the king, the Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The "White Beast Handler" Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the creature above him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That vision I saw before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it a {\i0}memory{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What... is {\b0}happening{\b1} to me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's Battle Tournament has come to a close with four Duelists advancing to the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Semi-Finals will take place tomorrow morning at the third and final Dueling arena, as we leave the Battle Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over and out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The third Duel arena"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're leaving\N Domino City altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the third arena is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could care less {\i1}where{\i0} the Semi-Finals take place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Let's make it to the Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... You and the\N other Yugi must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... A lot has happened today, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many people have gotten hurt from this tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know this\N fight would be so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's head to Mai's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, am worried\N about this poor woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I join you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat Malik for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you tell me to be stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't take much more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...! Bakura-{\i1}san{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who has fought...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't... the world I wanted to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we mustn't turn away from anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our world is full of sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are those who who reach out with open arms with hopes of merely catching a glimpse of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dating all the way back to Ancient Egyptian times,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,us Tomb Guardians have\N had countless losses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to protect our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Tomb Guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the great power kept within the Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're Malik's sister,\N aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Malik want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Malik's dark side want to take everyone's lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The chosen one, who houses the Pharaoh's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragic past of the Ishtar family!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Ishtar clan, are descendants of the Tomb Guardians
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who protected two Millennium Items and the location of the Pharaoh's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lived deep underground,\N away from the rest of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eldest sons of the clans had to undergo the Rite of the Tomb Guardians,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have the Glyphs of the Pharaoh's memory carved into their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the life imposed on my younger brother Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tragedy took place five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One year after Malik\N underwent the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said I'm {\b0}going{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik! Lower your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father should be\N asleep about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haven't we been planning this day for a while now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I pretend like I'm sleeping,\N Father will never notice I left the tunnels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if Father finds out,\N we're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That will mean you\N broke the law of the clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will never forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If anything happens,\N Rishid will take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister... I... want to see what it's like out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lady Ishizu... I will cover for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please make Lord Malik's\N wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's leave in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, hear me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After one hour, we will come back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in his entire life, Malik felt the light of the sun wrap around his entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is what the town is like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, don't go\N touching anything of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stepping on a book like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These pictures look so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that... thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey boy, is seeing a television that rare for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There were people walking and talking in that box!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The guy in the TV was riding some strange machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A motorcycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I go on living,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's no way I can ride a motorcycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't stay here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was our agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me keep this\N page with the motorcycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What'll we do if Father finds it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I've got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just don't let Father find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The nameless Pharaoh's soul is about to be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who {\b0}are{\b1} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomb Guardians... A fate of bloodshed and tragedy awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this tragedy is the Pharaoh's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seek out the Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Pharaoh's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That man has to be Shadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This man appears before anyone tied to the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke the laws of my clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By exposing Malik to the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our family was fated to walk on a road of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy had an ankh around his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looked a lot like the Rod and Tauk our family keeps secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never speak of what you saw here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just forget that today {\b0}ever happened{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything you saw in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that man just now as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we really have to go back down, don't we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, follow right behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister, just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big sister, what's... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a contraption\N on the back of the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was dark when we left,\N so I didn't notice it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Mal-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is punishment for breaking the law of our tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This pitiful servant has suffered first because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Malik, it's {\b0}your{\b1} turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik...! You lousy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You intend to defy me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}thank{\b1} you for killing off Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dear father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel so much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik... What's gotten into you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is {\b0}mine{\b1} from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mustn't! I forbid you to touch the Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think this thing accepts me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Put that down immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}SHUT UP ALREADY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, you {\b0}bastard{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik! What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You stay {\b0}out{\b1} of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You... aren't Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start with {\b0}your{\b1} bloodbath,\N my dear father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then...\N That girl's the only one left, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's still alive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Won't you stay dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rishid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mustn't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who caused this destiny was the soul of the great Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Pharaoh will revive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go search for the Pharaoh, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pharaoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...caused Malik and his family's tragedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter {\i1}what{\i0}\N reason he has for doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai's... fighting for her life as we speak because of Malik's Power of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Malik isn't {\i1}beaten{\i0}...\N Mai's life will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I entrust the cleansing of Malik's dark side to you people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there may still be a chance to save Malik from a future shrouded in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please use your\N strength to help Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The shipboard lights will be turned off at twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will all tournament participants please return to their rooms by that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll watch over Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get to sleep"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where are\N you guys goin' to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't stay {\i1}here{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves us with {\i1}your{\i0} room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya freakin' serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No helping it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave her to you. Shizuka, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I haven't forgotten our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time\N to fight you again comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go at you with everything I got, and I'll beat ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you ask Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0} if you and Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} will battle each other in the Final match?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't ask such outrageous things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer hold the\N power to see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment the future changed when I fought Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the Pharaoh's memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will need the remaining five Millennium Items and the three God Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This belonged to you originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, part of my mission as a Tomb Guardian has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back to\N your room before lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Night!\N-Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I have {\b0}two{\b1} Millennium Items...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all seven Millennium Items are fitted into the slab in the hidden temple in Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the other Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All souls have a place to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place... to return...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all the Millennium Items\N are gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to go to Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if your memory would return after we did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my duty as your vessel to help you get your memory back, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Finals will be held tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid... The darkness of death has come for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you are alive, it is an {\i1}inconvenience{\i0} to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a {\i1}friend{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}piece{\i0} of Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I forgot that he implanted a part of himself in Bakura
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when he brainwashed Bakura's vessel with the Millennium Rod's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let you kill Rishid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to keep up your end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking that Millennium Rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. You're a Millennium Item collector, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand it over quietly, I won't make you a part of my {\i1}collection of souls{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now... Shall I {\i1}tear you apart{\i0} like the {\i1}puzzle{\i0} you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stick around a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill Rishid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's {\i1}your{\i0} turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is {\i1}nothing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were chosen by the Millennium Items...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...must settle things in a {\i1}Dark Game{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}pleasure{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rule is, whoever loses {\i1}disappears{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,132)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to beat Malik's dark half,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} works together with the part of Malik within Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s vessel, in a Tag Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as always, the two wielders of a Millennium Item fight with a Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the loser's body is eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what kind of Duel is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s Life dropped, his body began to disappear...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"(Dark) Malik VS (Dark) Bakura"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
